  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Pilot study of a soft, flexible hydration sensor
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Assessment of accuracy and feasibility of a skin hydration sensor at detecting differences in
      skin hydration between skin affected by atopic dermatitis and areas not affected.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
